---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me - Ali Mansoor">
  <main>
    <h2 class="animate-fade-in">About Me</h2>
    <p class="animate-slide-up">
      I'm a Software Engineer with a passion for creating exceptional user experiences across mobile and web platforms. My journey began during my university years, where I discovered my love for <strong>Flutter</strong>—a powerful framework for cross-platform mobile development—and modern frontend frameworks like <strong>React</strong> and <strong>Next.js</strong>. Through rigorous self-study and hands-on professional experience, I have developed expertise in building scalable, production-grade applications with polished interfaces and optimal performance.
    </p>
    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      Over the past 3+ years, I have successfully delivered multiple enterprise-grade applications spanning diverse domains—from fintech (digital payment platforms) and EdTech (learning management systems) to e-commerce and utility applications. My professional experience includes collaborations with industry-leading organizations such as <strong>Paymo</strong>, <strong>The Essential Studio</strong>, and <strong>GRADE UP</strong>, where I progressed from Junior to Senior Developer roles, contributing to mission-critical features and architectural decisions across mobile and web platforms.
    </p>
    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      I am deeply committed to engineering high-quality, maintainable applications with exceptional user experiences. My core technical expertise spans <strong>Flutter</strong> for mobile development, <strong>React</strong> and <strong>Next.js</strong> for modern web development, <strong>RESTful APIs</strong>, <strong>state management</strong>, and <strong>scalable application architecture</strong>. I specialize in building responsive, performant frontend solutions that prioritize user experience, clean code principles, and modern development practices.
    </p>
    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      Beyond my professional responsibilities, I actively engage with emerging technologies and development methodologies, continuously refining my technical skills through open-source contributions and personal projects. I am an advocate for clean code principles, thoughtful design, and collaborative development practices that foster innovation and knowledge sharing within engineering teams.
    </p>
    <p class="animate-slide-up-delay">
      Outside of professional development, I maintain a balanced lifestyle through sports and recreational activities, including football, competitive gaming, table tennis, and fitness training—pursuits that reinforce my commitment to discipline and continuous improvement.
    </p>

    <div class="skills-section">
      <h3 class="animate-fade-in">Technical Skills</h3>
      <div class="skills-grid animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #007AFF;">Flutter</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #61DAFB;">React</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #000000;">Next.js</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #3178C6;">TypeScript</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #F1DB4D;">JavaScript</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #06B6D4;">Tailwind CSS</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #764ABC;">Redux</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #F16529;">REST APIs</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #00D9FF;">Dart</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #47A248;">Git</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #13C3E7;">State Management</span>
        <span class="skill-pill" style="--skill-color: #FF6B6B;">Responsive Design</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: var(--color);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  p {
    max-width: 90ch;
    color: var(--color);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  p a {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slideUp 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .animate-slide-up-delay {
    animation: slideUp 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .skills-section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .skills-section h3 {
    color: var(--color);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .skills-grid.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .skill-pill {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    background: rgba(var(--primary-rgb, 52, 81, 178), 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--skill-color, var(--primary));
    color: var(--skill-color, var(--primary));
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .skill-pill:hover {
    background: var(--skill-color, var(--primary));
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(var(--skill-color, 52, 81, 178, 0.3));
  }

  @media (max-width: 450px) {
    p {
      font-size: small;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .skills-section h3 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
    .skill-pill {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
